title: NDC Oslo 2024
eventShortDescription:
​NDC Oslo 2024 will be an in-person event, held 10-14 June 2024 at the Oslo Spektrum. It's a five-day event comprised of 2-days deep-dive workshops, followed by 3 conference days with multiple simultaneous tracks.

SSW & Tina are proud sponsors. SSW Chief Architect + Microsoft Regional Director Adam Cogan is one of the many speakers.

Meet us there! 🙂

Note: SSW does not host this conference.
